          "tz": -480
        },
        "subject": "LU-2622 cache: Don't use env under ll_releasepage",
        "message": "LU-2622 cache: Don't use env under ll_releasepage\n\nDue to the global nature of the cl_envs_guard lock, it's possible to\nhighly contend on the lock when under memory pressure, resulting is a\nsevere performance degradation. The env isn't actually used underneath\nthe ll_releasepage call path, so this patch simply uses a NULL pointer\ninstead of trying to acquire one from the cache.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly\nSigned-off-by: Prakash Surya <surya1@llnl.gov>\nChange-Id: Ie98c0bb2fd0c88241d230ba8cd5c847d5c741e16\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
